{"tid":1986723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"職工盟申請5月1日遊行 李卓人：勞工現時已是「水深火熱」","createTime":"2020-04-24T04:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T11:38:42.000Z","uid":166360,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"680d7cb9526d4071d1f4f3057dc10c28385f68ec","tid":1986723,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T04:35:09.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情持續，職工盟秘書長李卓人表示，已向警方申請在五一勞動節發起遊行，強調整個遊行都會保持社交距離，會按照限聚令4人一組遊行，到達終點時會分批離開。他又指，5月1日是一個重要的日子，因勞工現時已是「水深火熱」，希望可透過遊行去表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2626690/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%81%B7%E5%B7%A5%E7%9B%9F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B5%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%80%E6%9D%8E%E5%8D%93%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E7%8F%BE%E6%99%82%E5%B7%B2%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E6%B0%B4%E6%B7%B1%E7%81%AB%E7%86%B1%E3%80%8D?mtc=10009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2626690%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%259B%259F%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B5%25E6%259C%25881%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%258D%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%2598%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2586%25B1%25E3%2580%258D%3Fmtc%3D10009&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=dad84cd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2626690/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%81%B7%E5%B7%A5%E7%9B%9F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B5%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%80%E6%9D%8E%E5%8D%93%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E7%8F%BE%E6%99%82%E5%B7%B2%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E6%B0%B4%E6%B7%B1%E7%81%AB%E7%86%B1%E3%80%8D?mtc=10009</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n人哥，其實勞工「水深火熱」的一大原因是政府的限制