，如果你們的訴求包括&quot;撤回停業令&quot;和&quot;取消餐廳限制措施&quot;的話，相信會得到更多人的支持</strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:55:00.000Z","msg":"水深火熱 是因為政府唔肯封關<br />\n繼續比 大陸人帶病毒來香港<br />\n<br />\n撤回停業令 取消餐廳限制措施 &lt;&lt; 都係一樣治標唔治本"},{"pid":"e12fecdc11991a381b405489d7acd7770413ce3d","tid":1986723,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=82d1b90b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0a82252b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n&quot;現時本港大約有5%的患者需入住深切治療部，但當年沙士有四分一患者需深切治療部&quot;<br />\n&quot;現時很多仍然留院的病人都很精神，毋須利用儀器供氧，甚至可以在病房玩電話或做運動，只是等待病毒檢測呈陰性反應&quot;<br />\n&quot;病人失去味覺和嗅覺的情況都很短暫，亦只有少部分病人有肺部纖維化情況&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>都話左疫情被誇大啦</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245eac8621bd9607d60e308d1a57412009b817b9","tid":1986723,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:21:40.000Z","msg":"取消限聚令<br />\n根本香港人靠自律戴口罩洗手就夠抗疫<br />\n特登搞個限聚令出黎加強popo執法權，結果搞到經濟食屎"},{"pid":"3d15eb66c37bcf88d9b5ada76a342990e6b4e4ec","tid":1986723,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"245eac8621bd9607d60e308d1a57412009b817b9","tid":1986723,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:21:40.000Z","msg":"取消限聚令<br />\n根本香港人靠自律戴口罩洗手就夠抗疫<br />\n特登搞個限聚令出黎加強popo執法權，結果搞到經濟食屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"但連登仔似乎唔怕經濟食屎，是否已經準備好食草過活